<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.2">
<l>alaitta pēḻvāy vāḷeyiṟṟōr kōḷari yāyavuṇaṉ</l>
<l>kolaikkai yāḷaṉ neñciṭanta kūruki rāḷaṉiṭam</l>
<l>malaitta celcāt teṟintapūcal vaṉtuṭi vāykaṭuppa</l>
<l>cilaikkai vēṭar teḻippaṟāta ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the one with sharp claws who gouged out the chest of the demon,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one with the murderous hands</l>
<l>As a fierce lion with sword[-like] teeth [and] a quivering cavernous mouth,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain where never ceases the shouting of hunters</l>
<l rend="indent">with bows in hand,</l>
<l>As the voice of [their] powerful drum rages [in a] battle</l>
<l rend="indent">where they plunder passing caravans which fight [back].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
